@startuml
title BP-19 - Bill Cancellation

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|Finance Officer|
start
:Open student obligation;
:Request cancellation or deletion;

|Platform|
:Validate obligation belongs to tenant;
:Check payment allocations;

if (Payment allocation exists?) then (Yes)
  :Reject cancellation or deletion;
  :Return obligation already used error;
  stop
else (No)
  :Set status to CANCELLED or soft delete record;
endif

:Record audit trail;

|Parent Guardian|
:Cancelled bill no longer appears as payable outstanding;
stop

note right
Current endpoint:
DELETE /student-obligations/{id}
Recommended behavior:
Do not delete obligations with payment history.
end note
@enduml
